{
  "stem": "1338.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now as far as employment is concerned, needless to say, the ghetto-- well, not needless to say, let's say-- the ghetto evolved too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't in one decision what it will be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Reading about it today, I understand that there was a lot of question whether this ghetto will exist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether it will be liquidated now or a month or a year or something later, so it was all evolving.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now I'm not going to sit here and tell you the history of ghetto life because there are books written on it and chronicle.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I would leave it to those who want to read about that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All I say, that it did evolve and that employment, obviously there was none at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they started opening places for work for the German industry, whatever they do, mostly, first of all, the tailor shops and then the leather shops and then even lumberyards.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm bringing lumberyards up because we had a big problem with my father going and finding a job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father basically, while maybe being-- remarking about the philosopher next to him asking this philosophical question, why am I pushing it if my life is worth nothing, my father actually adopted the same philosophy.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He felt that his life was not worth anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was nothing to do with this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He didn't see at this age why he has to adapt to that thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in the 50s.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was in the 50s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was much older than my mother, much older, about 16 or 17.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother immediately started looking for her work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
